nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 169 is the 147th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the seventy-seventh published by Titan Magazines. It was released on October 25, 2016, including the exclusive fiction "Turning Point."

Star Wars Rebels returns! As the saga continues on TV with the latest season of Star Wars Rebels, the cast and crew report in with details on the new season! With Rogue One weeks away from release, Star Wars Insider previews the new movie. Plus: The heroic journey of Anakin Skywalker revealed!
